OL,3,CTackling the 'massive stigma' around
OL,4,Cmental health in the Valleys
OL,6,FA men's suicide prevention charity is
OL,7,Fhelping "tackle the stigma" around
OL,8,Ftalking about mental health in the
OL,9,FValleys.
OL,11,FAndy's Man Club has five groups across
OL,12,FWales, it aims to double that figure
OL,13,Fthis year in a bid to help more people.
OL,15,FMark Collins helped set up the Merthyr
OL,16,Fbranch, he knows only too well the
OL,17,Fimportance of having somewhere to be
OL,18,Fable to go and talk openly about
OL,19,Fwhat's on your mind.
