OL,4,Cmental health in the Valleys
OL,6,FHe told ITV Wales: "We have a problem
OL,7,Fas men, I think it's the different
OL,8,Fchromosomes that we have, that we
OL,9,Fdon't tell people our problems. We
OL,10,Fnever have. It is not the manly thing
OL,11,Fto do allegedly."
OL,13,FLike everyone at the club, Mark has
OL,14,Fhis reasons for being involved. His
OL,15,Fson Ceri took his own life on 17
OL,16,FOctober 2022. A talented musician he
OL,17,Fhad just turned 39 and posted
OL,18,Fphotographs on Facebook saying how
OL,19,Flucky he was to have such good people
OL,20,Faround him.
