OL,6,FThe following day, the popular former
OL,7,FCyfartha High School pupil, who had
OL,8,Fsung all over the world, took his own
OL,9,Flife.
OL,11,FSpeaking to us almost a year on he
OL,12,Facknowledges some people might find it
OL,13,Fdifficult to initially open up to
OL,14,Fstrangers, he admits he too was in
OL,15,Fthat position.
OL,17,FHe said: "On the first night, I had
OL,18,Fsecond thoughts about coming through
OL,19,Fthe door to the first meeting.
