OL,6,F"But I am so, so glad I did. Because
OL,7,Fpeople listen, people cry and people
OL,8,Fget very emotional.
OL,10,F"It's not all doom and gloom because
OL,11,Fthere is some great support from the
OL,12,Ffacilitators of the club.
OL,14,F"What goes on in that room stays in
OL,15,Fthat room and that's the way it should
OL,16,Fbe."
