OL,4,Cmental health in the Valleys
OL,6,FPublic Health Wales now publishes a
OL,7,Freal-time suspected suicide
OL,8,Fsurveillance report which aims to
OL,9,Finform prevention work across the
OL,10,Fcountry.
OL,12,FJosh attends the Andy Man's Club at
OL,13,FMerthyr Town FC and says it's great to
OL,14,Fspeak out without being judged. He
OL,15,Fsaid: "I think we just need to get
OL,16,Finvolved with charity and talk a lot
OL,17,Fmore, to be honest.
