OL,3,CTackling the 'massive stigma' around
OL,4,Cmental health in the Valleys
OL,6,F"I think there is a massive stigma
OL,7,Faround the Valleys - that people
OL,8,Fcannot talk and I think there is no
OL,9,Fstigma.
OL,11,F"Be yourself talk with whoever you
OL,12,Fcan. Our door is always open and you
OL,13,Fwill be welcomed straight away."
OL,15,FThe fear of "loneliness and isolation"
OL,16,Fis the biggest challenge anyone who
OL,17,Fstruggles with their mental health
OL,18,Fwill face, according to project and
OL,19,Fdevelopment manager Dan Rowe.
