OL,3,CTackling the 'massive stigma' around
OL,4,Cmental health in the Valleys
OL,6,FHe says "being judged by other people"
OL,7,Fis a big issue too, adding "these are
OL,8,Fcharacteristics which we find very
OL,9,Fprevalent in men".
OL,11,FBut Dan said: "When you come together,
OL,12,Fyou do talk about it and you realise
OL,13,Fthat there is an environment out
OL,14,Fthere, where it is ok to feel however
OL,15,Fyou do feel.
OL,17,F"You'll be supported and most
OL,18,Fimportantly you won't be judged. I
OL,19,Fthink that is one of the most powerful
OL,20,Fthings about Andy's Man Club."
