OL,6,FIf you have been affected by anything
OL,7,Fin this article, help and advice can
OL,8,Fbe found .
OL,10,FSamaritans is available day or night,
OL,11,F365 days a year. You can call them for
OL,12,Ffree on 116 123, email them at
OL,13,Fjo@samaritans.org, or visit
OL,14,Fwww.samaritans.org to find your
OL,15,Fnearest branch.
OL,17,FThe Mental Health Helpline for Wales
OL,18,Fis available to take your call any
OL,19,Ftime, day or night. Freephone 0800 132
OL,20,F737 or text 'help" to 81066 (charged
OL,21,Fat standard network rate)
